<div class="parental-consent-terms" style="align:left;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;width:80%;">
<p>
I give consent for my child, who is under 18 years of age, to participate in a photo shoot at The Photo Studio (and any further
photo shoots taken by The Photo Studio) and in so doing agree to be bound by the Terms and Conditions of this agreement
on my child's behalf. I confirm that as the parent I will attend the photo session and the I will attend the viewing session. If I
choose not to attend my child's viewing session and be present the entire time, I understand that it will be cancelled and I
agree to pay a non-attendance out-of-pocket fee of $200.00 to be charged against my valid credit card. I authorise The Photo
Studio to make the charge within 7 days of cancellation, and recognise that The Photo Studio is not obliged to re-book a
cancelled session. 
</p>


